<lyrics>[V1]
 Mifalia, ry sakaiza !
 Fa nahazo taom-baovao,
 Zanahary no mitaiza,
 Ka isaory sy hajao ;
 Mihirà sy mihobia,
 Jeso Tompo no derao ;
 Miravoa, mifalia,
 Velona aina hianao.
 Mifalia ry sakaiza !
 Fa nahazo taom-baovao
 Zanahary no mitaiza,
 Ka isaory sy hajao.

[V2]
 Izao no andro mampifaly,
 Andro lehibe anio,
 Dia hira mahafaly
 No hatao ankehitrio ;
 Zanahary no mitàna,
 Mifalia hianao ;
 Tonon-kira hoe : Hosana !
 No hatao atý izao.
 Mifalia, ..sns.

[V3]
 He ! Hosana, he ! Hosana
 Ho Anao, ry Tompo ô !
 Fihirana fiderana,
 No asandratray izao ;
 Dera, saotra, hery, laza,
 Ho Anao, Mpanjakanay ;
 Ho Anao anie ny haja,
 Raiso ho Anao izao.
 Mifalia, ..sns.</lyrics>
<title>Mifalia, ry sakaiza! FFPM746</title>
</song>